Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 五百祗先生 到秋天了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有秋天的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?秋天的气味?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点尘土味 有点阳光味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点凉凉的又好像很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是种让人感觉很怀念的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有记忆了还知道秋天的气味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊

Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:40.34,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}KTXP&SD字幕組

Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}该怎么办才好来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:40.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:40.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所当然的事情总是这么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:43.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:43.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}纷繁复杂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:46.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:46.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想开心的时候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:51.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:51.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的时候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:59.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:59.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常说愿望总会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:07.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:07.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是总会到底要多久　已经等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}张开双臂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:18.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:18.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:21.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:21.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告诉我在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:24.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:24.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}伤得满目疮痍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:34.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:34.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}几十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是这样还
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:41.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:41.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}难以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:45.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:45.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信着明天

